00:14:52.702 --> 00:14:55.760
So entering the Garrison to investigate
is what you called planning ahead?

00:14:56.100 --> 00:14:57.339
The Garrison matters

00:14:57.340 --> 00:14:58.940
I will handle myself.

00:14:59.450 --> 00:15:00.970
The Xiao family still needs you here.

00:15:01.512 --> 00:15:03.072
Do not risk yourself again.

00:15:08.512 --> 00:15:09.552
Very well.

00:15:10.062 --> 00:15:11.382
I will listen to you.

00:15:12.340 --> 00:15:13.699
Physician Xi said

00:15:13.700 --> 00:15:15.274
