00:15:15.275 --> 00:15:17.635
Lie down and sleep a while.

00:15:26.950 --> 00:15:28.461
It is too warm today.

00:15:28.462 --> 00:15:29.742
I cannot stand the heat.

00:15:30.020 --> 00:15:31.780
Fan me for a bit, will you?

00:15:35.100 --> 00:15:36.380
Young Master Xiao,

00:15:36.460 --> 00:15:38.100
you do know how to order people around.

00:15:38.285 --> 00:15:39.524
It is only early spring,

00:15:39.525 --> 00:15:41.205
and you want someone to fan you?

00:15:43.837 --> 00:15:45.316
What do you know?

00:15:45.317 --> 00:15:45.636
I…

00:15:45.637 --> 00:15:46.732
Fine.

00:15:47.020 --> 00:15:48.011
I will stay right here.

00:15:48.012 --> 00:15:49.311
Not going anywhere.

00:15:49.312 --> 00:15:51.672
I will have Xiang Lei
fetch a fan from storage.

00:16:07.587 --> 00:16:08.827
He fell asleep already?

00:16:09.020 --> 00:16:09.980
Of course.

00:16:10.662 --> 00:16:12.822
I, Xi Junning, never fail.

00:16:13.500 --> 00:16:15.780
But you doing all this for the Xiao family,

00:16:15.820 --> 00:16:17.100
is it really worth it?

00:16:19.420 --> 00:16:20.940
Do not think too highly of me.

00:16:21.580 --> 00:16:22.961
Only if the Xiao family stands,

00:16:22.962 --> 00:16:24.220
do I stand with them.

00:16:24.380 --> 00:16:25.857
Is that not so?

